{"tid":439186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中史明年成初中必修科　何漢權：會以中國人身分為光榮","createTime":"2017-10-17T14:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T06:31:50.000Z","uid":53379,"like":7,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec1caca191be63e6ba96dce68ff61b9487f8778","tid":439186,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中史明年成初中必修科　何漢權：會以中國人身分為光榮 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171017/s00001/9f9b7611e018917ea60e6360f122db76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171017%2Fs00001%2F9f9b7611e018917ea60e6360f122db76.jpg&h=61c6d5d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥在《施政報告》提出，將於2018/19學年落實中史在初中獨立成必修科。教育評議會主席何漢權認為，「如果有（中史獨立成必修科），我覺得佢會以中國人身分為光榮」。<br />\n<br />\n何漢權接受《港人講地》訪問指，提倡「港獨」人士，「對中華民族燦爛文化，對近代中國的苦難，因為無知，所以就會產生無情」。<br />\n<br />\n他從鴉片戰爭講起，到日本侵華等，「（中國）百年受到的屈辱，軍民的犧牲，終於可以脫離亡族亡國大危機，在全世界有舉足輕重地位」，反問「一個這樣的民族，這樣的國家，你還好意思去說『我要獨立』？」<br />\n<br />\n至於中史獨立成必修科，何漢權稱：「如果有的話，我覺得佢會以中華文化，以中國人的身分為光榮。」<br />\n<br />\n對於有憂慮會「洗腦」，何漢權指這些「政治攻擊」言辭，除了顯露對方無知，亦對中國歷史科教師、學生及中國「很不尊重」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171017/s00001/1508230190366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171017%2Fs00001%2F1508230190366&d=gyZJa1c7dB5TSZsP%2FLFtkJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=8f86dc50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171017%2Fs00001%2F1508230190366&h=92c846ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171017/s00001/1508230190366</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係有呢啲國家先攪到要獨立"},{"pid":"55f215365842cc3efc22480b0c2cfdbd69d87dec","tid":439186,"uid":21423,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94a436907458410b5a0940d875b0173be3a673fc","tid":439186,"uid":56878,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"讀完先憎"},{"pid":"f9f3bfb8c117a6f37e8a1668bc61dc630f3b16ca","tid":439186,"uid":44358,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"就係熟悉中國史，我先會以中蟈為恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffed928e18eaacc45f9b46024d981e93e37044d","tid":439186,"uid":35790,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"中國歷史即係中原歷史"},{"pid":"5680030642ddba950117ee156e8a3fd33ff65a50","tid":439186,"uid":522,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"會唔會講長春圍城 中共餓死幾十萬軍民"},{"pid":"9ce7ff0064617ed308bc3eb26e15971b1aeaa752","tid":439186,"uid":143454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12d6b4306a8af380185749d77fb7385050b110d1","tid":439186,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"鴉片戰爭個時邊有中國 ？"},{"pid":"8606b37895b4e9fd3d794c49a38e70414ba04051","tid":439186,"uid":78620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國歷史即係中原歷史</blockquote><br />\n成吉思汗一時係外族, 一時係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a40b0da5491a1598c3b548bb9cc88db3700242c","tid":439186,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"講得出中華民族，已唔洗理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1169aaabafb82ef17394731f8dd2c13142ce7b3","tid":439186,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國歷史即係中原歷史</blockquote><br />\n成吉思汗一時係外族, 一時係中國人<