ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"條友有份寫中屎書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69cae2e5e16724af26d660c566f4fb5878d0a8f","tid":439186,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"「中國」呢個詞語幾時產生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e020f5a705ecf2dae7044fe8f8a9598736677e6","tid":439186,"uid":125079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"至於中史獨立成必修科，何漢權稱：「如果有的話，我覺得佢會以中華文化，以中國人的身分為光榮。」<br />\n<br />\n我幾鍾意中史，都好有興趣去睇同學，但對依家共產黨管治緊既中國真係好反感，完全唔覺得光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5870d7d93d1763539381b7db87e5d799ef551d9a","tid":439186,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"南北朝後漢族<br />\n即係披上中原華夏文化外衣胡人或混血兒<br />\n大唐國李世民先祖係胡人"},{"pid":"0c722ca751c67d67e4ce6577179a8e611868fdc9","tid":439186,"uid":125079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:50:13.000Z","msg":"只有白痴先以為讀歷史會加深對個個國家既認同感，歷史係以前朝代，古代人既故事，近代中國歷史有文革，六四個啲搞成咁，你仲好意思拎出黎講，就算古代華夏文化幾勁幾好，關你依家垃圾共產黨咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1339dbb66adf7b710748237927630ca4cd437fac","tid":439186,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0ebddfe99a975847f1fb9e141d8ee7108dbb617","tid":439186,"uid":37232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"東北三省+沿海地區都應納入日本西征西狄史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6f3181a3fce84aafe8de2b20008a363f7bd9c6","tid":439186,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"一早要啦<